      "widgets_values": [
        "A beautiful young chubby princess wearing a flowing pink dress stands in a defensive stance, gripping an enormous longsword with both hands raised above her head. She has a determined, fierce expression on her round face, with her hair styled in two buns adorned with decorative netting or caps. Her body is positioned in a wide, grounded stance with legs apart for stability, weight shifted forward as she prepares to strike or defend. The princess wears a dress with puffy, rounded sleeves and a full skirt that billows around her substantial, curvy frame.\n\nTo her left looms a massive blue dragon's head, emerging from the upper portion of the frame at a downward angle. The dragon's elongated snout is open, revealing rows of sharp, pointed teeth as it exhales a stream of fire directly toward the princess. The creature has a single visible dark eye and is suspended from above by what appears to be a cord or rope. The dragon's neck curves dramatically as it angles its attack downward.\n\nBehind the princess, billowing smoke clouds rise and spread across the background, creating an atmospheric haze that suggests recent fire or explosive action. The ground beneath shows simple terrain lines indicating an outdoor battlefield setting. The composition captures a moment of high tension and confrontation, with the brave princess standing her ground against the fearsome dragon's fiery assault, sword ready to counter the monstrous threat."
